  "instructions": [
    "Heat the rendered pork fat in a large paella pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onions and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the mussels and cook until they start to open.",
    "Add the smoked salmon, Thai fish sauce, butter, white rice, lemon juice, black pepper, and chopped dill to the pan, stirring to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook, covered, for 25 minutes.",
    "Remove the pan from the heat and let it rest for 5 minutes before serving."
